    bf:note [ a bf:Note ;
            rdfs:label "Promotional pictorial map of the San Francisco Bay Area, from San Jose to Marin County, with portions of the East Bay included. Depicts area businesses involved with various aspects of the film industry in a cartoonish style. Aside from businesses, local landmarks such as the Golden Gate and Bay Bridges, the Bay Area's international airports, and sports stadiums are included."@en ],
